title: Academis - Community Sponsor of PyCon DE & PyData
---
full_description: Dr. Kristian Rother is developing Python since 2000. His training label Academis guides developers from programming fundamentals to professional software engineering practices. During courses, participants may expect a strong focus on hands-on coding exercises and interaction that enhances retention and keeps trainings enjoyable. Courses by Academis are exclusively in-person. In development projects, Kristian enjoys unmessing flaky test suites, refactoring legacy codebases and finding structure where the AI didn't.

